      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay i didnt know about that. the ttyl is a bit high though like 39C and he's really crying. if i can't use aspirin, can i just give him a double dose of ibuprofen to make sure it works faster? i have some extra strength stuff here so i was thinking a bit more might help him sleep.",
